</ul>
<p>Our client offer you a challenging position in an exciting, high-profile role. This is an opportunity to join a company where your creativity and expertise will be appreciated. This person will be instrumental in providing our client with a data environment that can grow with their business. With buy-in from senior management, you will have all the tools you need to be successful in this role.</p>', 'HuxleyIT', '', null, '2020-10-21 08:17:12.378039', '€70000 - €90000 per annum + competitive', 'Data Engineering Lead', 'HA-33558406', 'https://www.huxley.com/nl-nl/job/kyc/HA-33558406', '07587795-05bb-4718-ade4-a4498f1e7b78');
