<p>You will need to set up a data driven way of working in a digital training environment and drive global (learning) enhancement programs from behavioral insights and user validation.</p>
<p><strong><span>Tasks;</span></strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>You have a key role in gathering analyzing and using the data to drive leaning effectiveness for a new smart learning environment that provides certified training courses to employees in 20+ countries</li>
 <li>You build the bridge between business and the external smart learning environment.</li>
 <li>You are responsible for management reporting (execution and improvement). You optimize and automate the processes for integrated reporting and data, knowing how to include quality by design;</li>
 <li>You analyze and recommend strategies to enhance the end to end platform experience of the (digital) learnings</li>
 <li>You are key in driving the global roll out of learnings and activating &amp; motivating users. You analyze, report, prepare strategies, plan and coordinate with the rest of the roll out team how to increase completion rates.</li>
 <li>You set up user acceptance tests and you provide support &amp; execute on testing</li>
 <li>You prepare communication to different stakeholders</li>
 <li>You stimulate cross-border interaction and alignment between stakeholders;</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><span>Profile;</span></strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>We are looking for an energetic and driven expert with strong analytical capabilities who uses state-of-the-art methods and techniques for business analysis.</li>
 <li>You have a master or bachelor degree (IT, Engineering, Maths or Economics/Business is a plus);</li>
 <li>You have a minimum of 3+ years of working experience in financial or business analysis (Consulting experience is a big plus);</li>
 <li>You have proven experience in setting up steering dashboards by integrating data from different sources and formats, monitoring progress and trends and forecasting results. You are able to translate data into actionable insights and come up with strategies for realizing targets on completion and business improvements.</li>
