<p>As one of their Senior Java Developers you will be responsible for designing, developing and testing new and existing features on e.g. a high tech financial workflow system. The role will include working with complex technical data tools and require the right individual to have a strong command of core java and a good appreciation of latency sensitive systems.</p>
