INSERT INTO public.vacancy (id, about, broker, company, hours, posting_date, salary, title, vacancy_number, vacancyurl, location_id) VALUES ('fc189b99-939d-4b3d-b581-ca7264e7832b', '<b>In short</b>
<p>We’re looking for a senior full-stack developer to join our team and help drive our digital innovation agenda.</p>
<p>It doesn’t matter if you like front-end or back-end better, as long as you know your way around both. Your strong attention to detail, curiosity and value adding insights help to realize our goals. You are eager, can manage the diverse responsibilities and take pride and joy in delivering results. </p>
<p>Are you a team-player who is not afraid of pioneering and experimenting to deliver business value with a short time to market? Can you hit the ground running? Reach out!</p><b>Your work</b>
<ul>
 <li>Write working software to build our front-end and back-end capabilities</li>
 <li>You’ll be playing a big role in Requirements Engineering, Prototyping</li>
 <li>Write APIs and consume them</li>
 <li>Set up infrastructure and maintain it</li>
 <li>Analytics: measure all the things! (validation is the foundation of our work)</li>
 <li>Continuous improvement of our technology stack – each and every day</li>
</ul><b>Werkomgeving</b>
<p>Our ambition is to democratize financial planning, to give people convenient access to concrete &amp; tangible financial expertise. Expertise which is relevant and personal, addressing client needs and challenges. Without pushing products. We serve both Retail and Private Banking clients of ABN AMRO.</p>
<p>We operate in an “unknown problem, unknown solution” environment. As such we need developers with the ability to work intimately with proposition developers in a short cyclical and iterative approach with a close connection to our Dutch (speaking) clients.Developers that can join and contribute to design sprints and turn UX/UI designs and wireframes into front-to-back prototypes in 1 or 2 sprints.And if validated, can iterate the prototype to a shippable MVP.</p>
<p>Our team consists of proposition developers and IT engineers, all of whom share an end-to-end responsibility spanning both business and technology. There is one product owner and one product backlog. The propositions in scope of the team are digital first propositions, e.g. conversational dialogues, digital financial summary &amp; omnichannel financial planning. The team works based on Agile principles and is self-directed and is a growing BizDevOps teams.</p><b>Your profile</b>
<ul>
 <li>Full stack developer with at least 10 years of experience</li>
 <li>BSc or MSc in computer science or relevant field</li>
 <li>Knowledge of financial services and developments in the banking sector like Open Banking</li>
 <li>Experienced in developing software in general: CI/CD Pipelines, Container orchestration, Containers, Microservices</li>
 <li>Experienced in amongst others Java, JSON, REST, Javascript (Angular or Jamstack) and SQL</li>
 <li>Experience with Azure DevOps is preferred</li>
 <li>Live in the Netherlands; fluent in English &amp; preferably Dutch</li>
</ul><b>What we offer</b>
<p>We will give you the freedom to get the best out of yourself, work flexibly and have plenty of room to grow</p>
<p>•We help you to stay fit and healthy</p>
<p>•A salary between 65K and 90K based on a 36 hour working week. </p>
<p>•A supplementary benefit budget of 11% with which you can buy flexible fringe benefits</p>
<p>•A personal development budget of € 1,000 a year</p>
<p>•An annual public transport pass</p>
<p>•A generous pension scheme</p><b>Interested?</b>
<p>Are you interested? Apply online. For more information, reach out to Tamer Atwa, IT Engineering Lead Advice via tamer.atwa@nl.abnamro.com</p>   <strong>Type vacature:</strong>  Intern   Vaardigheden
