<p>You are experienced in:<br>• (complex) stakeholder management;<br>• working with user stories and preferably with customer journey’s;<br>• working in DevOps teams;<br>• managing complex IT Epics;<br>• working with the agile methodology.</p>
<p><br><b>What is required?</b></p>
<p>• A completed bachelor or academic education;<br>• Strong affinity with IT;<br>• Passion for innovation in customer communication;<br>• Excellent command of Dutch and English;<br>• An Orange Code behavior and mindset;<br>• A CX mindset.</p>
