<p>• A 36-hour working week;<br>• The position is classified in salary scale 10;<br>• Room to grow: both as CJE and in the Agile Way of Working;<br>• The location is preferably Leeuwarden, but you willing to travel to Amsterdam from time to time.<br></p>   <strong>Type vacature:</strong>  Intern   Vaardigheden
