 <li><p>You have frontend development experience with web components: HTML &amp; CSS, JavaScript, LitElement, lit-html </p></li>
 <li><p>You are experienced in Testing: Performance testing (Gatling, JMeter), End-to-end testing, Test automation (Cucumber, Selenium)</p></li>
