</ul>
<p>(If you don’t have these, we will facilitate you to develop yourself in these areas)</p>
<p><b>What we offer</b></p>
<p>Challenging projects &amp; extensive learning options, Personal development &amp; chapter time (10%) and personal coaching from chapter lead and expert team members.</p>
<p>To give you an idea, we will tell you about the benefits of working at ING:</p>
<ul>
 <li><p>A salary tailored to your qualities and experience</p></li>
 <li><p>Flexible working hours and the possibility to work at home</p></li>
 <li><p>Travel reimbursement</p></li>
 <li><p>27 vacation days with 40-hour work week</p></li>
 <li><p>Pension scheme</p></li>
 <li><p>13th month salary</p></li>
 <li><p>Individual Savings Contribution (BIS), 3.5% of your gross annual salary</p></li>
 <li><p>8% Holiday payment</p></li>
 <li><p>Personal growth and challenging work with endless possibilities</p></li>
 <li><p>An informal working environment with innovative colleagues</p></li>
 <li><p>Work Agile, so new ideas come to life faster</p></li>
 <li><p>Assistance with a transfer to NL (for Foreign Locals)</p></li>
</ul>
<p><b>Questions?</b></p>
